---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insights">
  <section class="bg-primary text-white text-center py-20 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Tech Insights & Thought Leadership</h1>
    <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">Stay ahead of the curve with our expert takes on technology trends, threats, and tactics.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <article class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded shadow hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">🔐 5 Essential Cybersecurity Practices in 2025</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">The top techniques SMBs need now to stay secure — firewalls are just the start.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-accent font-semibold mt-2 inline-block">Read More →</a>
      </article>
      <article class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded shadow hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">☁️ Should You Move to a Multi-Cloud Strategy?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">We break down when it's worth it, when it's not, and how to prepare.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-accent font-semibold mt-2 inline-block">Read More →</a>
      </article>
      <article class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded shadow hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">🚀 The IronLink Incident Response Checklist</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">When a breach happens, here’s what we do in the first 30 minutes — and what you should too.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-accent font-semibold mt-2 inline-block">Read More →</a>
      </article>
      <article class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded shadow hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">📊 IT Budget Planning for CEOs</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Smart spending doesn’t mean cutting corners — it means knowing where to invest.</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-accent font-semibold mt-2 inline-block">Read More →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>